data.title: 3rd LD Virtual Town Hall Tomorrow: Now at 7:00 PM – Marcus Riccelli
data.text:
Join me and my seatmates tomorrow, Thursday, March 24th for a Virtual Town Hall. The town hall will be streamed live on my legislative Facebook page at 7:00 PM.

Please note the new start time of 7:00 PM. We pushed the start back an hour to give everyone a chance to watch the Gonzaga Men’s Basketball Team’s Sweet 16 game. Go Zags!

What: 3rd Legislative District Virtual Town Hall

When: Thursday, March 24th at 7:00 PM

Where: Streaming live on my legislative Facebook page, as well as the Senate Democrats’ Facebook, Youtube, and Twitter pages.

You can submit questions in advance here or enter them in the comment section live during the town hall.
